Revision history for Net::JBoss

0.04    26 Nov 2015
        - fix typo on method name
        - add support to get stats for xa data source

0.03	29 May 2015
		- add SSL support

0.02	28 April 2015
		- reload, restart, shutdown JBoss instance
		- get application deployment info 
		- enable / disable pool statistics 
		- get application runtime statistics
		- test data source connection pooling
		- set data source min pool size
		- set data source max pool size
		- get jndi view
		- get and set log level
		
0.01    27 April 2015
        First version.

